Package: adRpheno
Title: Tools for Alzheimer's Disease Endophenotype Analysis
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ana", "Boeriu",
           email = "ana.boeriu@ucsf.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for standardizing and analyzing Alzheimer's Disease (AD)
    endophenotypes. Functions cover biomarker outlier detection and
    standardization, clinical measurement calculations (eGFR, BMI,
    blood pressure), cognitive composite score computation,
    APOE genotype validation and risk classification, and medication
    processing through the National Library of Medicine RxNorm and
    RxClass APIs with on-disk caching.
